txt.en: 'You ought to clear them out before you try to start fishing here.'
'Careful now! Great big snappers ahead -- turtles. They bite hard....'
'You don't want them chomping at your heels while you try to fish. Trust me.'
'Elhudan -- bog lights! You cannot fish with those nasty glares trying to lull you beneath the waters....'
'I will let you deal with them....'
'Yech, slugs! You had best squash them.'
'You are almost done! You just need to fish up one more relic.'
